ZH: 请如实告诉我你的名字。
EN: Please tell me your name truthfully.

ZH: 我会如实向你汇报我的工作进展。
EN: I will report my work progress to you truthfully.

ZH: 你应该如实回答老师的问题。
EN: You should truthfully answer the teacher's questions.

ZH: 他如实地描述了事故发生的经过。
EN: He truthfully described how the accident happened.

ZH: 她让我如实讲述了我的观点。
EN: She asked me to truthfully express my opinion.

ZH: 请如实告诉我你对这个计划的看法。
EN: Please tell me truthfully what you think of this plan.

ZH: 我们必须如实向客户解释清楚。
EN: We must truthfully explain to the customer.

ZH: 这份调查需要被如实回答。
EN: This survey needs to be answered truthfully.

ZH: 无论发生什么事情，我们都要如实面对。
EN: No matter what happens, we must face it truthfully.

ZH: 请如实告诉我你的打算。
EN: Please truthfully tell me about your plans.

ZH: 他果断地如实回答了问题。
EN: He decisively answered the question truthfully.

ZH: 我是说，我必须如实告诉你。
EN: I mean, I have to tell you truthfully.

ZH: 请如实告诉我你对这个决定的看法。
EN: Please truthfully tell me what you think of this decision.

ZH: 我应该如实和他们表达自己的观点。
EN: I should truthfully express my opinions to them.

ZH: 我会如实地向你讲述发生的一切。
EN: I will truthfully tell you everything that happened.

ZH: 无论结果如何，我们都要如实面对。
EN: Regardless of the outcome, we must face it truthfully.

ZH: 我希望你能如实告诉我真相。
EN: I hope you can truthfully tell me the truth.

ZH: 如果你不如实回答，会有后果的。
EN: There will be consequences if you do not answer truthfully.

ZH: 请如实汇报你的工作情况。
EN: Please truthfully report your work situation.

ZH: 他始终如实告诉你实情。
EN: He always truthfully tells you the truth.
